sections.footer.about:
Experience Moroccofresh - for agriculture.

Whether you are a livestock farmer or a farmer, a contractor or a forester: In the BayWa portal you will find a wide range of animal feed, seeds and crop protection - conventional or ecological - for agriculture. In addition, you will receive detailed information about our diverse advisory services, services, events and topics as well as about us, your BayWa.
Discover our diversity - digitally and on site
